headline: Sysco (SYY) Valuation Check After Higher Profit Outlook And Strong Quarter
summary: Sysco (SYY) recently raised its full year profit outlook after second quarter results came in ahead of expectations, as strong demand for steaks, fillets and frozen food met tighter control of shipping and supplier costs. See our latest analysis for Sysco. That stronger profit guidance and steady foodservice demand sit alongside a 30 day share price return of 18.27% and a year to date share price return of 24.11%.
